        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="It's official ! We've linked up with Love Island's
Chloe Burrows and she's the first ever face of JD Women!

You'll all know Chloe from this year's Love
Island line - up.  She's funny , infectious and all
about the positive vibes ! Not stopping there ,
this gal knows her stuff when it comes to the
latest trends and what to be seen in. From chill
day looks to the latest trainers that she's obsessin ' over , she's
the ultimate go - to for style inspo "
        android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
        android:textSize="20sp"
        android:textColor="@color/darkblue"


